- Got it.
- When you see it.

37:05.033 --> 37:06.467
- Amazing.
- We're looking forward to it.

37:06.500 --> 37:08.066
Thank you.
- Okay. Awesome.

37:08.100 --> 37:11.200
[upbeat music]

37:11.200 --> 37:13.333
- Oh, nice.

37:13.333 --> 37:15.467
- Oh, beautiful.
- Fantastic.

37:15.467 --> 37:17.333
- Love another coffee, please.
- Cool, thank you.

37:17.367 --> 37:18.734
- Pleasure.

