37:46.633 --> 37:48.300
it might be too much
to ask at this stage.

37:48.333 --> 37:50.734
Captain Sandy, tender is away.

37:50.767 --> 37:52.700
Max, hold on.

37:52.734 --> 37:54.767
- Bobby, Bobby, Sandy.
Ready to take the anchor up.

37:54.767 --> 37:57.734
- Copy that,
pulling the anchor up now.

37:57.767 --> 38:00.100
Anchor's in the pocket.

38:00.100 --> 38:02.367
♪ ♪

38:02.400 --> 38:05.233
- You look so cute,
and I'm like a big, sloppy mess.

38:05.233 --> 38:06.633
- You've got a great body.

38:06.633 --> 38:08.600
You should be wearing bikinis
and rocking it.

38:08.633 --> 38:10.000
- You're a lawyer,
not a model.

