38:22.400 --> 38:24.667
Chain gang.

38:24.667 --> 38:31.166
♪ ♪

38:36.667 --> 38:39.400
- Oh, my God.

38:39.400 --> 38:41.667
Oh, my God,
this is magnificent.

38:41.667 --> 38:44.400
- Here she is.

38:44.400 --> 38:45.667
- Wow.
- Look at this.

38:45.667 --> 38:48.400
This is insane.
- Unbelievable.

38:48.433 --> 38:51.333
- It's stunning.

38:51.367 --> 38:54.467
- Drop the starboard anchor
60 meters.

38:57.400 --> 38:59.000
- Keep going, keep going.

38:59.033 --> 39:01.500
Bobby, come ground here.
- Good job, Bobby.

39:01.533 --> 39:04.000
- All right, we have got
the starboard line on the winch.

