I could get fired for.

39:13.300 --> 39:15.133
- Tender is heading
to the port line.

39:15.166 --> 39:16.700
- Got it.

39:16.700 --> 39:19.133
- Yeah, all right.
Foredeck, foredeck.

39:19.166 --> 39:21.033
We've got tension
on port side,

39:21.033 --> 39:23.000
and we've got quite a lot
of tension on starboard side,

39:23.033 --> 39:24.700
and I think
if you guys are happy

39:24.700 --> 39:26.500
we're gonna lock it off there,
we're lined up nicely.

39:26.533 --> 39:28.567
- Excellent job, guys.
That was like pros.

39:28.600 --> 39:30.700
- Thank you, Captain.

39:32.667 --> 39:34.600
- Is lunch ready or something?
- At 1:30.

39:34.600 --> 39:37.467
- We've got some of the guests
at the table here.

39:37.500 --> 39:39.467
- I love the decorations.
- It's so pretty, right?

39:39.500 --> 39:41.734
- What a centerpiece.
- Quick, quick, quick, quick.

39:41.767 --> 39:43.467
Okay, good.
- Thank you very much.

39:43.467 --> 39:44.600
- Golden.
- Wanna take this one?

39:44.633 --> 39:46.266
- Yep.

39:47.333 --> 39:49.467
[beeping]

