39:53.333 --> 39:55.200
- Holy sh--, you're right.

39:55.200 --> 39:57.333
- Bugs, can you come to
the galley and help me ASAP?

39:57.367 --> 39:59.266
Please!
- Get a bucket.

39:59.300 --> 40:01.066
- Yeah?

40:01.100 --> 40:02.467
[beeping]

40:02.467 --> 40:04.066
- What's going on?

40:04.100 --> 40:06.333
- The sink is overflowing.
