- Thanks, Hannah.

40:18.100 --> 40:19.500
- Okay, okay, okay.

40:19.533 --> 40:21.633
- Here we go.

40:21.633 --> 40:25.066
- Yep.
Right here.

40:25.100 --> 40:26.166
- So good.

40:26.200 --> 40:28.166
- So fresh and healthy.

40:28.200 --> 40:30.100
[beeping]

