in that tender and push.

41:46.400 --> 41:47.567
- Okay.

41:47.600 --> 41:50.400
- 'Cause I gotta
figure this out.

41:52.300 --> 41:54.667
Max, come push.
Max, Max.

41:54.700 --> 41:57.567
- Yeah, go ahead.
